WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 7]

01:44.310 --> 01:45.820
When the world just began,

01:46.230 --> 01:47.460
Pan Gu's spirit

01:47.870 --> 01:48.980
became the Dragon Deity.

01:50.120 --> 01:51.670
He had nine sons.

01:51.840 --> 01:53.260
Calamity came from Jiu Ying.

01:54.040 --> 01:54.820
Jiu Ying

01:55.200 --> 01:56.270
was the lord of all demons.

01:56.790 --> 01:57.850
He plunged the world into chaos,

01:58.870 --> 02:01.290
and sparked endless war between men and demons.

02:01.440 --> 02:02.980
Bodies covered the land.

02:04.160 --> 02:06.390
To save all living beings,

02:06.750 --> 02:08.690
the nine dragon sons fought Jiu Ying to the death.

02:09.400 --> 02:10.610
Eight of them

02:11.080 --> 02:12.810
turned into towering mountains

02:13.110 --> 02:14.410
to seal Jiu Ying away.

02:15.560 --> 02:17.220
Only the ninth son,

02:17.510 --> 02:18.330
Chi Wen,

02:18.800 --> 02:20.050
remained in the world

02:20.550 --> 02:22.210
to guard all life.

02:39.180 --> 02:43.940
[Ten years ago]

02:55.940 --> 03:01.740
♪Step by step in endless woe♪

03:02.420 --> 03:08.860
♪Hearts have a home, but bodies none♪

03:09.860 --> 03:16.380
♪Fate rises and falls, I let it go♪

03:16.380 --> 03:20.980
♪If dreams end as one, why fear the road?♪

03:23.780 --> 03:24.660
Who are you?

03:25.510 --> 03:26.420
Where are you from?

03:30.230 --> 03:31.240
I don't remember.

03:32.830 --> 03:33.580
What's your name?

03:36.160 --> 03:37.300
You don't remember your name either?

03:42.920 --> 03:43.930
What do you remember then?

03:47.000 --> 03:47.860
I think...

03:50.880 --> 03:52.050
I have a younger brother.

03:56.340 --> 03:58.580
Why were you outside the Shilin Sect?

04:00.950 --> 04:01.900
I don't know.

04:06.040 --> 04:07.370
I just felt...

04:08.280 --> 04:10.140
a voice calling me.

04:11.950 --> 04:13.210
It told me to come here.

04:16.350 --> 04:17.050
That's fine.

04:19.200 --> 04:20.330
You can stay here.

04:21.620 --> 04:28.140
♪So many dawns and dusks in pouring rain♪

04:28.500 --> 04:31.100
♪Twilight weighs down beyond our sight♪

04:31.100 --> 04:34.980
♪Trapping us small souls so tight...♪

04:35.920 --> 04:36.970
Fierce wind, driving rain.

04:38.600 --> 04:39.850
Reborn after calamity.

04:41.750 --> 04:42.730
I'll name you after this image...

04:46.310 --> 04:47.020
Li Jie.

04:48.990 --> 04:50.170
Li Jie...

04:54.550 --> 04:55.580
You're very strong.

04:56.790 --> 04:57.970
The Shilin Sect has no weapon

04:57.990 --> 04:58.770
fit for you.

05:00.190 --> 05:01.170
Go to Mount Nandang.

05:02.110 --> 05:02.930
A long knife

05:02.930 --> 05:04.290
left behind by a mountain demon

05:05.600 --> 05:06.850
is stuck at its peak.

05:07.550 --> 05:09.020
No one has been able to pull it out.

05:09.990 --> 05:10.770
Give it a try.

06:07.230 --> 06:07.900
Ji Ling.

06:20.550 --> 06:22.530
The Shilin Sect is a terrible place.

06:23.790 --> 06:25.240
Chained by spells,

06:25.600 --> 06:26.700
caged by wards.

06:28.230 --> 06:30.120
They don't just strip demons of their painted human skins,

06:32.110 --> 06:33.880
but also change the hearts of people.

06:40.620 --> 06:41.720
Feeling guilty?

06:43.110 --> 06:44.950
My lofty Master Dragon Deity?

06:45.920 --> 06:46.850
I like you more

06:46.870 --> 06:48.020
when you're Ji Ling.

06:49.160 --> 06:50.020
To me,

06:52.600 --> 06:54.060
innocent, sweet Ji Ling

06:54.520 --> 06:55.410
is much more interesting.

06:58.520 --> 06:59.580
A fox from the Formless Moon,

06:59.640 --> 07:00.620
do you even have a heart?

07:02.190 --> 07:04.210
You dare speak of "like"?

07:06.990 --> 07:07.700
A heart?

07:09.110 --> 07:10.140
Of course I have.

07:13.280 --> 07:15.320
If you can't feel it,

07:16.230 --> 07:17.260
you can touch it and see.

07:23.240 --> 07:24.820
Are you shy now?

07:25.870 --> 07:27.880
We shared so much at the Wei mansion.

07:28.480 --> 07:29.450
Have you forgotten?

07:32.350 --> 07:33.580
Or maybe...

07:36.040 --> 07:36.770
you're afraid of me?

07:46.040 --> 07:47.090
You are Ji Ling.

07:48.520 --> 07:49.140
Why else

07:49.920 --> 07:51.380
would you suddenly show up

07:51.920 --> 07:54.090
and free me from all these spells?

07:57.640 --> 07:58.900
You couldn't bear to see me hurt.

08:00.040 --> 08:01.210
Couldn't bear to see me scarred.

08:02.870 --> 08:04.010
The wound on your neck

08:04.040 --> 08:04.970
looks pretty deep.

08:05.520 --> 08:06.970
If you don't treat it properly,

08:07.400 --> 08:08.330
it will leave a scar.

08:09.430 --> 08:10.090
Am I right?

08:12.870 --> 08:13.730
Since ancient times,

08:14.990 --> 08:16.460
the Formless Moon and Shilin Sect

08:16.840 --> 08:17.700
keep out of each other's way,

08:18.310 --> 08:19.210
each showing great restraint.

08:20.110 --> 08:21.210
If a Formless Moon fox

08:21.870 --> 08:23.620
dies in the Shilin Sect's hall,

08:24.600 --> 08:25.460
that's a headache

08:26.350 --> 08:27.210
I don't want.

08:32.400 --> 08:33.380
I'll overlook

08:34.080 --> 08:34.850
your trespassing.

08:35.640 --> 08:36.900
I'll have someone escort you out.

08:38.070 --> 08:38.770
And take this.

08:41.360 --> 08:42.450
You risked coming here

08:43.240 --> 08:44.930
surely for this thing, right?

09:05.120 --> 09:06.770
What if I have another purpose?

09:08.040 --> 09:09.770
What if I want to stay with you?

09:16.240 --> 09:17.140
Master,

09:18.640 --> 09:20.220
you bathe and scent yourself every day?

09:22.760 --> 09:24.050
This fragrance on you is so unique.

09:24.640 --> 09:26.650
I've never smelled it anywhere else.

09:28.360 --> 09:29.410
But this smell...

09:31.760 --> 09:33.650
leaves my heart feeling empty,

09:34.830 --> 09:38.290
like a valley full of flowers

09:38.430 --> 09:39.980
but empty of people.

09:44.160 --> 09:45.050
Master,

09:51.310 --> 09:52.740
are you lonely?

09:56.430 --> 09:58.220
Want me to stay with you?

10:08.040 --> 10:09.360
Such a bad act.

10:10.240 --> 10:11.410
Stop pretending.

10:12.830 --> 10:14.140
Formless Moon foxes

10:14.640 --> 10:16.500
excel at fake feelings

10:17.670 --> 10:18.770
and word manipulation.

10:19.760 --> 10:20.620
To get what they want,

10:21.070 --> 10:22.450
they wear a thousand faces

10:22.950 --> 10:24.770
and whisper sweet nothings.

10:25.790 --> 10:27.570
Under such a pretty face,

10:29.430 --> 10:31.170
what a cold heart hides.

10:32.190 --> 10:33.570
You know it well yourself.

10:37.830 --> 10:38.690
You too.

10:39.760 --> 10:41.410
Under such a pretty face,

10:41.950 --> 10:43.810
what a cold heart hides.

10:45.400 --> 10:46.770
You know it well yourself.

10:55.670 --> 10:56.690
You are not Ji Ling!

10:58.040 --> 10:59.260
You've got your jade jue back.

11:01.070 --> 11:02.380
If you don't want to fade away,

11:03.590 --> 11:05.340
take this token and leave.

11:47.310 --> 11:47.930
You're awake?

11:50.670 --> 11:51.770
I'm in the Shilin Sect?

11:52.070 --> 11:52.620
Yeah.

11:52.880 --> 11:53.860
Are you feeling better?

11:55.100 --> 11:55.770
Ji Ling...

11:57.400 --> 11:58.340
really is the Dragon Deity?

11:59.000 --> 11:59.910
To be honest,

12:00.360 --> 12:01.410
this is our first time

12:01.430 --> 12:02.810
seeing Master's true form.

12:03.790 --> 12:05.220
Even you can't recognize the Dragon Deity?

12:05.640 --> 12:06.310
Master Chi Wen

12:06.310 --> 12:07.620
stays in the Scale Cave all year.

12:07.950 --> 12:08.880
Only Commander Li

12:08.880 --> 12:10.430
and his personal attendants serve him.

12:10.760 --> 12:11.810
How could ordinary hunters like us

12:12.040 --> 12:12.900
ever get to see him?

12:13.590 --> 12:14.770
But, come to think of it,

12:15.040 --> 12:16.930
the flowerless young hunter Ji Ling,

12:17.360 --> 12:18.410
who always joked with us

12:18.670 --> 12:20.290
and hunted demons by our side,

12:20.590 --> 12:21.690
turned out to be the Dragon Deity himself.

12:29.070 --> 12:29.860
Master,

12:30.590 --> 12:31.290
the new puppet is here.

13:41.920 --> 13:42.650
Master!

14:00.550 --> 14:01.860
Master, you're so powerful!

14:03.160 --> 14:04.500
No matter how badly I'm hurt,

14:05.160 --> 14:06.220
you can heal me completely,

14:07.120 --> 14:08.900
without even leaving a scar.

14:09.790 --> 14:10.530
But...

14:12.120 --> 14:14.050
I let you down this time.

14:14.670 --> 14:15.740
I failed my mission

14:16.160 --> 14:16.980
and didn't bring Xiaowei here.

14:18.760 --> 14:20.170
You did very well.

14:21.760 --> 14:22.690
Get some rest.

14:23.920 --> 14:24.650
Next,

14:25.160 --> 14:26.290
more important tasks

14:26.590 --> 14:27.450
await you.

14:29.670 --> 14:31.140
Whatever the mission,

14:31.470 --> 14:32.900
I'll give it my all!

14:41.190 --> 14:41.810
Oh, right.

14:42.230 --> 14:43.680
Xiaowei gravely wounded me.

14:44.670 --> 14:46.410
What about Miss Lu and her partner?

14:47.160 --> 14:48.020
Were they hurt?

14:48.520 --> 14:49.860
They've returned to the Formless Moon.

14:54.160 --> 14:54.770
Lu Wuyi

14:55.360 --> 14:56.980
just left this place.

15:05.710 --> 15:06.380
Master,

15:06.950 --> 15:08.620
if there's nothing else,

15:09.040 --> 15:09.900
I'll take my leave now.

15:10.710 --> 15:11.380
Go on.

15:12.040 --> 15:12.650
Wait.

15:21.200 --> 15:22.160
Thank you, Master.

15:22.280 --> 15:22.900
Go on.

15:33.880 --> 15:34.930
What are you worried about?

15:37.310 --> 15:38.810
I'm afraid that naive boy

15:40.070 --> 15:41.050
has fallen in love.

15:43.950 --> 15:44.770
Love?

15:46.880 --> 15:48.620
A puppet that was made,

15:49.640 --> 15:50.450
how could he feel love?

15:52.160 --> 15:53.340
But he's always believed

15:54.160 --> 15:55.810
he's a little fox

15:56.710 --> 15:58.380
you saved at the foot of South Mountain.

16:03.550 --> 16:05.340
Then let him keep believing.

16:07.240 --> 16:08.020
What's wrong with that?

16:09.640 --> 16:11.410
He's just a simple puppet with no heart,

16:12.360 --> 16:14.570
and she's just a demon fox with no feelings.

16:25.140 --> 16:28.500
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

16:29.100 --> 16:32.500
♪You brave the wind and bear the rain♪

16:33.020 --> 16:39.820
♪Thank you for the shelter of your shade♪

16:41.140 --> 16:44.660
♪Moon sets, crows cry...♪

16:45.040 --> 16:45.740
Wangyan.

16:47.720 --> 16:48.540
This is far enough.

16:48.990 --> 16:50.500
Safe travels, ladies.

16:51.400 --> 16:52.290
Thank you, sir.

16:54.760 --> 16:55.170
Wait.

16:56.950 --> 16:57.500
Miss Lu,

16:58.190 --> 17:00.220
you need to return that token.

17:38.510 --> 17:39.380
Lu Wuyi?

17:41.510 --> 17:42.140
Lu Wuyi?

17:43.430 --> 17:44.010
Lu Wuyi?

17:45.510 --> 17:46.930
Lu Wuyi?

17:50.150 --> 17:50.940
Lu Wuyi?

17:50.940 --> 17:52.380
♪One winter day♪

17:52.780 --> 17:56.940
♪By the lake, a boy in white opened his eyes...♪

17:58.990 --> 17:59.810
Should we stop?

18:03.310 --> 18:04.050
Lu Wuyi?

18:09.200 --> 18:10.020
Lu Wuyi?

18:10.020 --> 18:15.860
♪He bowed low, gently offering wildflowers from his heart...♪

18:17.160 --> 18:17.980
Lu Wuyi?

18:18.380 --> 18:22.540
♪Each careful stroke carried a tiny wish...♪

18:26.110 --> 18:27.090
Lu Wuyi?

18:28.920 --> 18:29.980
We're just passing strangers.

18:31.040 --> 18:32.540
We can't even tell what's real.

18:33.280 --> 18:34.130
Why stop?

18:39.600 --> 18:40.730
Lu Wuyi...

18:41.940 --> 18:44.620
♪Tears shining in his eyes♪

18:44.700 --> 18:48.100
♪Step by step, he called and cried...♪

18:48.110 --> 18:49.090
Lu Wuyi...

18:49.100 --> 18:54.420
♪Yet fate fills his bowl of hope with regrets and sighs♪

18:54.700 --> 18:57.940
♪Longing drifts away like threads in the wind♪

18:58.180 --> 19:01.220
♪Like a small boat leaving the shore at night♪

19:01.580 --> 19:07.500
♪The wind takes pity and makes me turn and see♪

19:07.900 --> 19:13.540
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

19:13.980 --> 19:20.140
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

19:20.580 --> 19:21.980
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

19:22.140 --> 19:23.700
♪Bitter and sweet♪

19:23.900 --> 19:27.060
♪The moon stays by my side♪

19:27.500 --> 19:33.300
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

19:40.380 --> 19:47.300
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

19:47.310 --> 19:48.190
Miss Lu,

19:48.480 --> 19:49.290
there you are.

19:57.520 --> 20:00.980
Why are you wearing that robe?

20:04.120 --> 20:05.410
That annoying Dragon Deity

20:05.750 --> 20:06.850
ruined my clothes.

20:07.350 --> 20:08.540
Then, afraid people would gossip,

20:09.520 --> 20:11.060
he had his attendant

20:11.560 --> 20:12.980
give me this ugly robe.

20:16.000 --> 20:17.130
That robe...

20:19.280 --> 20:20.410
is mine.

20:23.470 --> 20:24.170
Is it?

20:29.430 --> 20:30.060
Here you are!

20:50.280 --> 20:51.100
Your hands are dirty

20:52.680 --> 20:53.780
from picking flowers.

20:56.590 --> 20:57.540
It's fine!

20:58.750 --> 20:59.700
You said

21:01.190 --> 21:02.610
you love flowers most.

21:04.630 --> 21:05.500
So I picked some.

21:06.870 --> 21:08.380
You remember I love flowers?

21:13.560 --> 21:14.940
The mighty Dragon Deity

21:15.470 --> 21:16.890
stooped so low

21:17.800 --> 21:18.890
as to pick flowers himself?

21:20.720 --> 21:21.450
I...

21:22.400 --> 21:23.700
I'm not...

21:24.400 --> 21:25.330
I know you're not.

21:26.400 --> 21:27.220
You're Ji Ling.

21:33.750 --> 21:35.010
Sure, I love flowers...

21:37.680 --> 21:38.820
but out here,

21:39.150 --> 21:40.610
they're all over the hills.

21:42.350 --> 21:44.010
You ran all the way here, out of breath.

21:45.590 --> 21:46.410
It wasn't worth it.

21:47.310 --> 21:48.010
No, it was.

21:48.800 --> 21:50.170
These only bloom

21:50.170 --> 21:51.940
in the Shilin Sect.

21:52.310 --> 21:53.010
They're different.

21:53.840 --> 21:54.890
After you go back,

21:56.030 --> 21:57.570
when you see these flowers,

21:57.870 --> 21:58.780
maybe...

22:00.150 --> 22:01.380
they'll remind you of me.

22:11.020 --> 22:12.500
Flowers are pretty...

22:15.110 --> 22:16.620
but they'll wilt soon.

22:19.350 --> 22:20.130
We can't keep them.

22:23.230 --> 22:24.210
Even if I miss you,

22:25.340 --> 22:26.570
it won't last...

22:27.520 --> 22:28.210
more than a few days!

22:30.280 --> 22:31.130
That's okay.

22:31.760 --> 22:32.500
Next time,

22:33.400 --> 22:34.210
I'll make you

22:34.230 --> 22:35.770
a flower that never wilts.

22:36.280 --> 22:36.970
Deal?

22:38.960 --> 22:39.650
Next time?

22:41.200 --> 22:42.180
Anyway,

22:43.440 --> 22:44.740
we will meet again,

22:45.320 --> 22:45.890
won't we?

22:50.910 --> 22:51.820
Then I'll wait for it.

22:57.500 --> 22:59.540
♪Watch the daylight♪

22:59.980 --> 23:02.220
♪Slowly hiding the moon from sight♪

23:02.740 --> 23:06.940
♪See dewdrops swaying in a dream tonight♪

23:08.380 --> 23:09.380
♪My beloved♪

23:09.740 --> 23:13.500
♪Holds flowers, waiting through the pouring rain♪

23:14.020 --> 23:19.060
♪No words, no questions♪

23:20.020 --> 23:21.820
♪At the edge of the world♪

23:21.940 --> 23:23.140
♪Someone counts their wishes...♪

23:23.280 --> 23:24.970
How... will I find you then?

23:26.200 --> 23:26.940
Don't worry.

23:27.760 --> 23:28.570
I'll find you.

23:31.260 --> 23:33.020
♪Petal after petal falls...♪

23:33.670 --> 23:34.300
Miss Lu,

23:34.670 --> 23:36.010
your boat is already gone.

23:36.550 --> 23:37.890
I'll call another one for you.

23:38.520 --> 23:39.330
Miss Lu...

23:42.020 --> 23:44.500
♪Who is chasing step by step♪

23:44.820 --> 23:47.220
♪Smiling at the days gone by?♪

23:47.220 --> 23:50.460
♪The curved moon so longs♪

23:50.780 --> 23:52.740
♪To be with her for all eternity♪

23:52.780 --> 23:55.980
♪No pain, no tears, she takes it all in stride♪

23:56.060 --> 23:58.260
♪Facing the light, she's brave inside♪

23:58.380 --> 24:03.860
♪Who remembers dewdrops fade at dawn's light?♪

24:04.500 --> 24:07.180
♪Under the world's small roof♪

24:07.940 --> 24:10.940
♪You're right here by my side♪

24:11.700 --> 24:15.260
♪Flowers blooming far and wide♪

24:16.220 --> 24:21.900
♪How sweetly we smile♪

24:21.910 --> 24:22.650
You like him?

24:25.590 --> 24:27.010
I just like flowers.

24:35.510 --> 24:36.380
You can't keep them.

24:42.120 --> 24:42.930
I know.

25:08.200 --> 25:08.990
Oh man!

25:08.990 --> 25:10.690
How did the Dragon Deity's Power get into you?

25:16.430 --> 25:17.100
Where are we?

25:18.880 --> 25:19.650
We're in the Shilin Sect.

25:23.080 --> 25:24.100
We're done for.

25:25.320 --> 25:26.900
Chickens in a weasel's den!

25:27.670 --> 25:28.380
Yeah, you're one.

25:33.160 --> 25:34.060
I've never seen

25:34.320 --> 25:35.580
that six-eyed butterfly demon before.

25:36.360 --> 25:38.300
He calls himself Yuan Wuhuo.

25:44.320 --> 25:45.450
Yuan Wuhuo?

25:45.950 --> 25:46.620
Yes.

25:47.510 --> 25:48.730
That name sounded

25:48.750 --> 25:49.780
kind of familiar.

25:50.270 --> 25:50.900
So,

25:50.950 --> 25:52.250
I went to Wanlin Pavilion

25:52.670 --> 25:54.340
and looked through the sect archives.

25:55.320 --> 25:55.860
Sure enough,

25:56.040 --> 25:57.150
a hundred years ago,

25:57.400 --> 25:59.410
a hunter commander in our sect

26:00.160 --> 26:01.170
also named Yuan Wuhuo.

26:02.030 --> 26:02.730
However,

26:03.160 --> 26:04.250
his name meant "no calamity."

26:05.120 --> 26:06.900
Just one character different from the butterfly demon's.

26:22.750 --> 26:23.860
Commander Yuan Wuhuo

26:25.600 --> 26:26.490
passed away long ago.

26:28.030 --> 26:28.900
But there's something strange

26:28.920 --> 26:30.450
about Yuan Wuhuo this time.

26:32.080 --> 26:32.860
He looks...

26:33.920 --> 26:34.730
exactly like

26:35.600 --> 26:36.580
Commander Li Jie.

26:40.880 --> 26:42.820
I heard Commander Li lost his memory

26:43.670 --> 26:45.300
and has never found his past.

26:46.400 --> 26:47.450
Could the two of them

26:48.750 --> 26:50.170
be connected somehow?

26:52.470 --> 26:53.340
One's a demon,

26:53.920 --> 26:54.780
one's a human.

26:55.920 --> 26:57.100
How could they be connected?

26:58.270 --> 26:59.680
When a demon takes human form,

26:59.720 --> 27:01.250
the first skin they paint

27:01.510 --> 27:03.340
is often made from something

27:03.340 --> 27:04.340
lost by a human.

27:05.430 --> 27:07.180
So they take on the owner's appearance.

27:08.070 --> 27:09.510
Maybe this butterfly demon

27:09.670 --> 27:11.720
found something from Li Jie,

27:12.560 --> 27:14.300
and took his form.

27:16.230 --> 27:16.930
Fair enough.

27:19.990 --> 27:20.780
For now,

27:22.030 --> 27:23.340
let's keep this from Li Jie.

27:26.030 --> 27:26.650
Yeah.

27:27.920 --> 27:29.300
If that stern commander of ours

27:29.670 --> 27:30.860
found out some demon

27:31.120 --> 27:32.540
borrowed his face,

27:33.080 --> 27:33.820
he'd probably

27:34.750 --> 27:35.690
explode with rage.

27:42.640 --> 27:43.380
Master.

27:44.120 --> 27:44.650
You're here.

27:45.510 --> 27:46.300
Mr. Bai Ze,

27:47.710 --> 27:48.580
what brings you here?

27:49.880 --> 27:51.340
I know all things in the world.

27:52.800 --> 27:54.380
Something's troubling my master.

27:56.190 --> 27:57.410
I'm here to help.

27:58.840 --> 28:00.380
Master, you want to ask

28:01.430 --> 28:02.580
why the Dragon Deity's Power

28:03.400 --> 28:05.010
got into Wu Shiguang, right?

28:06.190 --> 28:06.900
Why?

28:09.080 --> 28:09.730
Because of this.

28:12.600 --> 28:13.690
That string of prayer beads?

28:14.270 --> 28:15.140
What's their story?

28:16.600 --> 28:18.250
They're called the Twelve Thoughts.

28:18.990 --> 28:20.900
Each bead is made from a dragon fang,

28:21.640 --> 28:23.490
so they can carry sinners' blood

28:24.880 --> 28:25.970
and the Dragon Deity's Power.

28:27.120 --> 28:27.900
I'm guessing

28:29.030 --> 28:30.250
the Dragon Deity's Power

28:30.250 --> 28:31.650
must've sensed the dragon aura

28:32.990 --> 28:34.300
and was drawn to them.

28:35.950 --> 28:37.380
So it's thanks to the dragon fangs.

28:38.720 --> 28:40.540
They were your master's legacy, right?

28:42.750 --> 28:43.820
He was really something,

28:45.190 --> 28:46.620
stealing teeth from a dragon!

28:48.160 --> 28:49.340
So many dragon fangs...

28:50.260 --> 28:52.210
Wu Shiguang is just a folk hunter.

28:53.120 --> 28:54.340
Where could he have gotten them?

28:55.800 --> 28:57.540
The first owner of the Twelve Thoughts,

28:58.470 --> 28:59.370
legend says,

28:59.370 --> 29:01.100
was a corrupted demon monk.

29:02.030 --> 29:02.620
Mo Yuntan,

29:03.190 --> 29:04.410
continue gathering

29:04.640 --> 29:06.010
the spirit fragments of Jiu Ying.

29:06.560 --> 29:07.300
I have other matters

29:07.640 --> 29:09.010
to discuss with Bai Ze.

29:10.920 --> 29:11.540
Yes, sir.

29:12.360 --> 29:13.300
Maybe soon,

29:14.640 --> 29:16.160
all you double-flower hunters

29:16.160 --> 29:17.500
can lay down your burdens

29:18.470 --> 29:20.540
and stop toiling across

29:20.670 --> 29:21.490
this vast land.

29:35.560 --> 29:36.820
It's not because of those prayer beads.

29:38.510 --> 29:39.210
I know.

29:41.230 --> 29:41.970
This day...

29:44.430 --> 29:45.650
has finally come.

30:15.820 --> 30:19.300
[The Dragon Deity will fall. The Formless Moon will rise.]

30:21.030 --> 30:21.970
"The Dragon Deity will fall."

30:22.920 --> 30:24.210
"The Formless Moon will rise."

30:35.320 --> 30:36.650
After Jiu Ying was sealed,

30:36.920 --> 30:38.010
the demons lost their leader

30:38.510 --> 30:39.380
and scattered across the land.

30:40.160 --> 30:41.450
Many of them

30:42.120 --> 30:43.650
are lurking and scheming

30:44.080 --> 30:44.970
to free Jiu Ying.

30:47.080 --> 30:48.140
The one

30:48.160 --> 30:49.970
behind Xiaowei's broken vow

30:51.120 --> 30:52.690
is after the Dragon Deity's Power.

30:53.670 --> 30:55.010
Only that power

30:55.190 --> 30:56.450
can kill a dragon.

30:57.360 --> 30:58.410
And the last fragments

30:58.600 --> 31:00.010
of the Dragon Deity's Power

31:01.080 --> 31:03.170
reside in you four high-rank demons.

31:04.080 --> 31:05.970
Whoever gathers all four first

31:07.190 --> 31:08.250
can kill the dragon.

31:09.640 --> 31:10.780
If the Dragon Deity falls,

31:12.560 --> 31:13.900
Jiu Ying's seal will shatter,

31:15.030 --> 31:16.450
and chaos will consume the world.

31:18.510 --> 31:19.100
So...

31:20.080 --> 31:21.030
is Wu Shiguang the one

31:21.030 --> 31:22.100
we've been waiting for?

31:23.880 --> 31:24.960
You could say yes,

31:27.510 --> 31:28.490
but also no.

31:30.840 --> 31:31.650
Hide them already.

31:33.560 --> 31:35.010
We've sneaked in now.

31:35.470 --> 31:36.410
What's the next move?

31:37.670 --> 31:38.210
Wait.

31:38.950 --> 31:39.490
Wait?

31:42.990 --> 31:43.930
Wait for the right moment

31:44.990 --> 31:45.860
and do our best.

31:48.430 --> 31:49.410
"Do our best"?

31:51.320 --> 31:52.450
Isn't that my family motto?

31:53.120 --> 31:54.100
You sure remember it well.

31:56.560 --> 31:57.410
How come you remember it so well?

32:00.880 --> 32:02.020
Some things...

32:08.030 --> 32:08.960
are different now.

32:10.080 --> 32:11.250
So what's your plan?

32:12.600 --> 32:13.820
I've sent Li Jie and Ji Ling

32:13.820 --> 32:15.010
to retrieve the prayer beads.

32:17.560 --> 32:18.730
I want him to know

32:20.430 --> 32:21.970
I refuse to remain

32:21.990 --> 32:23.410
a powerless Dragon Deity.

32:25.640 --> 32:27.540
I'll take back my supreme power.

32:29.600 --> 32:32.210
I want people to worship me for all eternity,

32:35.430 --> 32:36.620
to revere me as a god.

32:37.670 --> 32:38.410
Wu Shiguang?

32:39.710 --> 32:40.900
See? Opportunity knocks.

32:51.190 --> 32:52.880
Master, you're here

32:53.640 --> 32:55.780
to take back your power from me?

32:58.190 --> 32:58.780
I...

32:58.950 --> 32:59.540
Hand over the prayer beads.

33:02.040 --> 33:03.820
Since you want them,

33:06.360 --> 33:07.810
I should return them sincerely.

33:08.630 --> 33:09.340
Don't worry.

33:10.000 --> 33:11.820
Once we extract the power inside,

33:12.030 --> 33:13.060
we'll give the beads back to you.

33:16.840 --> 33:17.580
Stop right there!

33:25.120 --> 33:25.970
I've waited for this moment...

33:28.270 --> 33:29.380
for far too long.

33:31.950 --> 33:33.490
If I'd known you were the Dragon Deity,

33:35.400 --> 33:36.790
I would have killed you

33:37.840 --> 33:38.970
back at the Wei mansion.

33:56.030 --> 33:56.780
He scared me to death!

33:57.190 --> 33:58.060
Hey, you fight dirty!

34:01.400 --> 34:02.730
Don't... don't kill me!

34:08.990 --> 34:09.580
Stop!

34:32.950 --> 34:33.500
Demon marks!

34:35.950 --> 34:36.660
You're a demon?

34:38.870 --> 34:41.170
Wu Shiguang is the sole survivor

34:41.950 --> 34:43.100
of the flood dragon clan's massacre.

34:44.350 --> 34:45.450
So he's here

34:46.760 --> 34:47.970
to avenge his people?

34:52.200 --> 34:52.820
That's right.

34:54.110 --> 34:54.820
I am a demon,

34:58.510 --> 34:59.380
one of the flood dragon clan.

35:00.800 --> 35:02.700
Back then, you sent Shilin Sect hunters

35:03.320 --> 35:05.050
to slaughter all my kin.

35:12.720 --> 35:14.180
You claimed to end the war

35:15.680 --> 35:17.450
between men and demons,

35:17.990 --> 35:18.740
but in secret,

35:19.360 --> 35:21.050
you feared Jiu Ying would break free

35:21.760 --> 35:22.970
and let the demons rise.

35:24.200 --> 35:25.970
So you ordered hunters

35:26.760 --> 35:28.010
to wipe out every demon clan

35:28.880 --> 35:30.010
in advance!

35:32.110 --> 35:34.300
The Dragon Deity wiped out your clan?

35:37.360 --> 35:37.900
What's wrong?

35:39.920 --> 35:41.820
You killed too many demons

35:42.720 --> 35:43.530
to remember this massacre?

35:50.840 --> 35:51.700
Since you're a demon,

35:52.430 --> 35:53.260
I can't let you keep

35:53.320 --> 35:54.300
the Dragon Deity's Power.

35:56.880 --> 35:57.530
Hand over the beads,

35:58.030 --> 35:58.700
and I'll let him go.

36:07.920 --> 36:09.300
"The Dragon Deity will fall."

36:11.030 --> 36:11.930
Master,

36:12.840 --> 36:13.700
you once said

36:13.990 --> 36:15.780
only a dragon can kill a dragon.

36:16.400 --> 36:18.820
The eight dragon sons sacrificed themselves,

36:18.820 --> 36:20.070
standing as mountains.

36:20.720 --> 36:22.180
Only Chi Wen remains.

36:23.280 --> 36:25.990
Who is left to kill him?

36:26.880 --> 36:28.490
Whoever holds

36:29.110 --> 36:30.610
the Dragon Deity's Power.

36:31.920 --> 36:33.610
Now, Chi Wen's under siege

36:34.920 --> 36:36.490
from his own former power.

36:59.360 --> 37:00.340
According to the Oracle Stone's

37:00.400 --> 37:01.380
latest prophecy,

37:03.240 --> 37:04.450
Wangyan and I

37:04.970 --> 37:06.530
are going to protect

37:06.630 --> 37:07.260
the Dragon Deity?

37:08.920 --> 37:09.450
No.

37:11.080 --> 37:12.590
You're going to kill him.

37:17.030 --> 37:19.150
The Dragon Deity represents divine justice,

37:19.320 --> 37:20.470
truth and goodness in this world.

37:21.030 --> 37:22.260
Why kill him?

37:22.720 --> 37:24.050
A single thought

37:24.630 --> 37:25.990
can twist a deity into a demon.

37:26.590 --> 37:27.340
Chi Wen

37:28.030 --> 37:29.860
once cared for all beings.

37:30.760 --> 37:34.190
But now corrupted by Jiu Ying's taint,

37:34.840 --> 37:36.130
he feeds on them.

37:40.030 --> 37:40.610
Spare me!

37:40.760 --> 37:42.780
I... I don't know anything!

37:44.220 --> 37:45.500
Please!

37:45.510 --> 37:46.800
Let us go!

37:46.800 --> 37:49.870
I need to see my grandson!

37:50.590 --> 37:51.780
It hurts!

37:52.590 --> 37:55.260
Mother, save me!

37:58.240 --> 37:59.400
Peace in this world

37:59.920 --> 38:01.720
often comes at the cost of sacrifice.

38:02.360 --> 38:03.340
Chi Wen's fall

38:04.200 --> 38:05.030
perhaps

38:05.550 --> 38:06.900
is for a new balance.

38:08.150 --> 38:10.490
You two must aid the dragon slayer,

38:10.680 --> 38:11.630
gather his power,

38:11.950 --> 38:13.050
and restore order to the world.

38:13.590 --> 38:14.820
Right now, the most urgent thing

38:15.440 --> 38:17.220
is to find the remaining high-rank demons

38:17.800 --> 38:18.860
and take back from them

38:18.910 --> 38:19.690
your power.

38:20.710 --> 38:21.420
I know.

38:22.790 --> 38:24.050
We've waited so long.

38:25.350 --> 38:26.890
Finally, this chance has come,

38:28.240 --> 38:29.610
a chance to rightfully take back

38:29.610 --> 38:30.860
my own power.

38:32.710 --> 38:33.580
This mission

38:35.760 --> 38:37.260
must not fail.

38:43.360 --> 38:45.380
Once I gather all four demons' power,

38:45.990 --> 38:47.010
I can slay the dragon myself.

38:47.510 --> 38:48.820
Why rely on someone else?

38:49.720 --> 38:50.660
The Dragon Deity's Power

38:51.320 --> 38:52.740
can only be held by the ancient stone,

38:53.150 --> 38:54.570
the Spirit-Storing Jade.

38:55.430 --> 38:57.930
The jade was split in two by heavenly fire

38:58.360 --> 38:59.450
and forged into magical tools.

39:00.200 --> 39:00.930
One piece

39:01.150 --> 39:02.920
is the Spirit-Storing Butterfly

39:02.950 --> 39:03.780
held by the six-eyed butterfly demon.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.340
The other piece

39:05.800 --> 39:07.570
is the Spirit-Binding Ring

39:08.880 --> 39:09.700
worn on the Dragon Deity's hand.

39:13.430 --> 39:14.410
Let me wipe your hands.

39:14.950 --> 39:15.930
They're all dirty.

39:19.920 --> 39:20.740
So...

39:21.950 --> 39:24.090
we just need to take the ring.

39:26.590 --> 39:27.780
After all these centuries,

39:28.400 --> 39:29.700
you're still like a child,

39:29.990 --> 39:31.050
so willful.

39:32.470 --> 39:33.450
If you want to try,

39:34.720 --> 39:35.740
go ahead.

40:03.840 --> 40:04.410
You Chi!

40:24.150 --> 40:24.570
Ji Ling!

40:26.840 --> 40:27.410
Hide!

40:39.720 --> 40:40.970
This is... wood!

40:42.920 --> 40:44.090
But how can wood bleed?

40:49.070 --> 40:49.740
I don't get it.

40:50.590 --> 40:51.700
What's going on?

40:53.840 --> 40:55.090
So you're a puppet.

41:01.280 --> 41:02.530
You're not the Dragon Deity at all!

41:16.630 --> 41:17.300
Li...

41:19.880 --> 41:20.820
Li Jie...

41:38.460 --> 41:39.620
♪It's your light♪

41:39.820 --> 41:41.700
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

41:41.860 --> 41:44.980
♪That set the night alight♪

41:45.340 --> 41:51.860
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:53.620 --> 41:55.500
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:55.940 --> 42:00.380
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

42:01.180 --> 42:02.860
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

42:03.020 --> 42:08.420
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

42:09.180 --> 42:14.580
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

42:16.900 --> 42:22.940
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

42:23.900 --> 42:26.060
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

42:26.340 --> 42:31.180
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

42:31.540 --> 42:33.860
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

42:34.060 --> 42:39.140
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

42:39.380 --> 42:41.380
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

42:41.660 --> 42:46.020
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:47.020 --> 42:53.980
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

43:10.540 --> 43:13.500
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

43:14.580 --> 43:17.980
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

43:18.780 --> 43:21.300
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

43:21.540 --> 43:24.620
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

43:25.020 --> 43:27.340
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

43:27.860 --> 43:32.260
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

43:32.500 --> 43:34.660
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

43:35.060 --> 43:40.020
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

43:40.260 --> 43:41.420
♪It's your light♪

43:41.620 --> 43:43.460
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:43.660 --> 43:46.780
♪That set the night alight♪

43:47.540 --> 43:56.980
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
